Alex Smith Occupation Job title Third year medical student Portrayer Shane Van Dyke Information First Seen Season 7 Episode 2 Sleeping Murder Last Seen Post Series TV Movie: Diagnosis Murder: Without Warning Appeared 13 episodes as a recurring character in seasons 7 & 8 and one TV movie as Alex Smith; Shane Van Dyke also appeared in three earlier episodes as different guest characters in seasons 4, 5, & 6.

Alex Smith, the third year medical student at Community General Hospital who appears in roughly 14 episodes of the series.

He is also seen as a boxing student in Never Say Die (this episode stars the rest of Barry Van Dyke's children also.)
